{"tid":906673,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇中大出身既徐立之？","createTime":"2018-11-18T07:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T08:43:43.000Z","uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3678384b69e3feda39eb3bb4aa7329872786646a","tid":906673,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa900d76c965e3b096d356e49e8b376c63c24fa","tid":906673,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"點睇港大出身既沈祖堯?"},{"pid":"7435ce3e4f12dc3d2a1216c8cd148f3dd826679c","tid":906673,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa900d76c965e3b096d356e49e8b376c63c24fa","tid":906673,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"點睇港大出身既沈祖堯?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"由於不懂得考試技巧，升中時他只考進中文中學 ── 巴富街官立中學，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">進不了香港大學</span></span>，他要當建築師的願望難圓。老師說他分析力強，就是不勤力，其實他是勤力的，只是不背死資料。考試前，同學都致電求教，電話多得父親罵他整天講電話。他為同學一一解答疑難，但考試成績卻不及他們好。雖然考試老吃虧，但徐立之常說他幸運﹕「我真的是一世好運。有天時，地利，人和，往往路走到那裡，那裡就行得通。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.com.cuhk.edu.hk/ubeat_past/021253/tsui.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.com.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fubeat_past%2F021253%2Ftsui.htm&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2aaac0c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.com.cuhk.edu.hk/ubeat_past/021253/tsui.htm</a>"},{"pid":"56a0a2a0ab55196b381e61d8ea4eda17ad8810d7","tid":906673,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7435ce3e4f12dc3d2a1216c8cd148f3dd826679c","tid":906673,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa900d76c965e3b096d356e49e8b376c63c24fa","tid":906673,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"點睇港大出身既沈祖堯?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:54:5